      <title>昆巴铁矿石考虑因物流限制而裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/kumba-iron-ore-considers-job-cuts-on-logistics-constraints</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 的南非铁矿石部门已提议进行重组，由于物流瓶颈限制了其出口能力，这可能会影响约 490 个工作岗位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/kumba-iron-ore-considers-job-cuts-on-logistics-constraints</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 06:17:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国担忧升级，铁矿石跌至三个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/iron-ore-slumps-to-three-month-low-as-china-concerns-escalate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中国房地产市场获得额外支持，但铁矿石价格仍跌至三个月低点，原因是投资者担心春节假期后钢铁需求不会强劲复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/iron-ore-slumps-to-three-month-low-as-china-concerns-escalate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 03:45:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中资银行大幅下调关键利率以支持房地产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/chinese-banks-cut-mortgage-reference-rate-by-most-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国加大了对陷入困境的房地产行业的支持力度，对关键抵押贷款参考利率进行了有史以来最大幅度的下调，这提高了人们对未来几个月采取更积极措施支持经济的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/chinese-banks-cut-mortgage-reference-rate-by-most-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 01:21:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>再次红海袭击后油价维持近三个月高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在胡塞武装再次袭击红海后，油价保持在三个多月来的最高水平附近，原油生产和贸易关键地区的紧张局势继续发酵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 23:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票和美国期货在谨慎交易中回落：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中国采取了最新措施支持陷入困境的房地产行业，但由于全球市场弥漫着谨慎情绪，欧洲股市和美国股指期货下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 22:58:37 GMT</pubDate>
